---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <section class="blogs-container">
        <h1>My Blog</h1>
        <p>Welcome to my blog! Here I share my thoughts and experiences on software development, books, and more.</p>

        <ul class="blog-list">
            <li>
                <div class="blog-header">
                    <a href="/blogs/enhancing-api-gateway-nginx-lua" class="blog-title-link"><strong>Enhancing API Gateway through OpenResty and Lua</strong></a>
                </div>
                <p class="blog-date">September 20, 2020</p>
                <p class="blog-summary">In this post, I discuss various enhancements to an API Gateway using OpenResty and Lua, including public URL management and user archiving.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="blog-header">
                    <a href="/blogs/building-api-gateway-nginx-lua" class="blog-title-link"><strong>Building an API Gateway with Nginx + Lua</strong></a>
                </div>
                <p class="blog-date">October 23, 2019</p>
                <p class="blog-summary">In this post, I explore how to build an API gateway using Nginx and Lua, leveraging the power of OpenResty.</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    .blogs-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .blog-list {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        list-style-type: none;
        padding-left: 0;
    }

    .blog-list li {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    .blog-list li:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
    }

    .blog-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: baseline;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .blog-title-link {
        color: #0066cc;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .blog-title-link:hover {
        color: #004d99;
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .blog-date {
        color: #666;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin: 0.25rem 0;
    }

    .blog-summary {
        margin: 0.5rem 0 0 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
</style>